The most Irresponsible and talented guy i have ever seen. Being your roommate for 3 years we ppl(all 10) have enjoyed so much but when we went over line and wanted to play one more game you were the guy who normally stopped. 
We will spend another year together(if this corona permits) but the memories we have spent together the minimilitia we played together and every other game you were the one guy whom i would say i had the most fun playing with as you were equally strong to me in most of them.
You excelled in cricket and studies which mattered the most. 
It was nice knowing you bro! 
Best wishes
